TTG Asia takes a break as Singapore heads to the polls Singapore, September 10, 2015 
TTG Asia e-Daily will be taking a break for the public holiday on Friday, September 11. 

In a statement by Singaporeâ€™s Elections Department on August 25, it was announced that Polling Day during any general election shall be made a public holiday.
